entries.title_d: Hunt Down the Hidden Daggers Leaders
entries.title: Corellia System: Duty: Strike a blow to the Hidden Daggers Leadership.
entries.taunt_5: I have crushed greater things than you CorSec! In fact, I shot a Womprat back on Tatooine last week!
entries.taunt_4: You're fighting a uphill battle CorSec, and the hill just got steeper!
entries.taunt_3: You CorSec always have to interfere, well this time you stuck your nose too deep!
entries.taunt_2: I will shred your ship CorSec fool!
entries.taunt_1: You think you can match the Hidden Daggers? I think not!
entries.targets_detected: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Vessels fitting hunted ship profile on attack vector, weapon systems armed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.targets_behind: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Be aware, vessels trying to target this ship with their weapon systems. Attack originating direction 180 degrees.\#pcontrast3  >
entries.quest_location_d: Dynamic sorties throughout the Corellia System
entries.level_increase: The Hidden Daggers are sending more reinforcements in responce to our attacks.
entries.level_boss_dead: Amazing! The Hidden Daggers will not forget this day. Stand by for further orders.
entries.level_boss: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Hidden Daggers has sent %TO to bring you down, proceed with caution. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc: New coordinates of pirate activity has been uploaded to your nav computer. Go get them!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_5: I've never seen those moves from a  CorSec before. No matter, prepare to die!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_4: Your flying skills remind me of a one winged Mynock!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_3: The cat becomes the mouse. The tables are turned, CorSec scum!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_2: Your just another kill mark on my ship, CorSec!
entries.complete: Fantastic job pilot, we struck a huge blow to the Hidden Daggers today. Return to base for a well earned rest.
entries.boss_detected: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Vessel with veteran insignias on attack vector, weapon systems armed. \#pcontrast3 >
